Introduction
************

   `Please dont forget to read the frequently asked questions!  Thank
You!'

   DLDialog was mainly developed for the `Deutsche Linux Distribution
(DLD) of delix Computer GmbH'.

   DLDialog offers the capability to draw a variety of widgets, in
order to ease the human user in feeding input to the script.  The
program is designed to be particularly useful to implement system
administration scripts.  I hope you will enjoy this program.

   `Harald Hoyer' harald@delix.de Hoyer@Royal.Net


