Normal compilation procedure
----------------------------

     $ aclocal
     $ autoheader
     $ automake -a
     $ autoconf
     $ ./configure --prefix=/usr

   If you do have kdoc installed:
     $ make

   else:
     $ cd src;make

   To install type:
     $ su -c "make install"

   If you want to deinstall it just do a:
     $ su -c "make uninstall"


